{"tid":2215114,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇歌令到你每次都心噏","createTime":"2020-09-23T18:27:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T15:49:40.000Z","uid":373590,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"7bc829508212b05c4d2c7ca9299299ca6de55305","tid":2215114,"uid":373590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:27:05.000Z","msg":"我先我先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/tq9j0E6XsGI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ftq9j0E6XsGI&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=86d5ede8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/tq9j0E6XsGI</a><br />\n成隻碟都好高質 每次凌晨時分好似特別有共鳴<br />\n獨愛sidetrack<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3bc6b8761eea91b038c53f585b0394d74f26cb","tid":2215114,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"義勇軍進行曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6feb293038a32eca18fcd49edee7d8de5001bf0","tid":2215114,"uid":373590,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"7e3bc6b8761eea91b038c53f585b0394d74f26cb","tid":2215114,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:37:25.000Z","msg":"義勇軍進行曲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T18:46:51.000Z","msg":"挽到咁deep㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其他人好難接"},{"pid":"0fe48f1be13135296f7db2fede2f371982d27d81","tid":2215114,"uid":112000,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:17:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3AUtk1wJJBc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3AUtk1wJJBc&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=ab648cd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3AUtk1wJJBc</a><br />\n<br />\nAll I Want - Kodaline"},{"pid":"90801025831998a3b2ef53bcbfd80f6d37bd9a52","tid":2215114,"uid":364552,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:30:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/6L4-VLWjHdA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F6L4-VLWjHdA&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=06200015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/6L4-VLWjHdA</a>"},{"pid":"4ff3857a67e81b85fe361863c9a251048cb73986","tid":2215114,"uid":42313,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:36:45.000Z","msg":"富士山下<br />\n<br />\n完全係我經歷緊既事，我曾經對「他」好執著，有日佢係ig story post左呢首歌，話給「to her,wish you all the best」，我就估到係比我了，了解左歌詞之後，明白呢首歌係佢心聲，表達對我執著既無奈，聽親我都好up，反省番我既執念為佢帶來左困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />愛佢，其實唔應該再逼佢番轉頭<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「怎麼始終牽掛 苦心選中今天想車你回家」</strong><br />\n當時我地大家都完左，雖然我係佢面前扮到好冷靜，但其實佢知我內心係海嘯緊。<br />\n<br />\n後尾佢搵我話有野同我講，結果佢都係講唔出口，我永遠記得個條路好似行足成個鐘咁，依家我諗佢都係想叫我開心啲掛。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>「原諒我不再送花 傷口應要結疤 花瓣鋪滿心裡墳場才害怕」</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如若你非我不嫁 彼此終必火化 一生一世等一天需要代價</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>情人節不要說穿 只敢撫你發端 這種姿態可會令你更心酸</strong><br />\n<br />\n所以我明佢點解咁絕<br />\n<br />\n<strong>我絕不罕有 往街里繞過一周 我便化烏有</strong><br />\n<br />\n曾經我都以為搵唔番好似佢咁好條件既人，原來香港地其實好多高質男<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03c3b9ee04655ca80f77406597006b8111a942ec","tid":2215114,"uid":369040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:38:12.000Z","msg":"愛得太遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n來日別操心　趁你有能力開心 <br />\n世界有太多東西發生　<br />\n不要等到天上俯瞰"},{"pid":"80d903e94d96d7d01c488c4bdf03f4fd4ee5633d","tid":2215114,"uid":34962,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:45:11.000Z","msg":"後來的我們<br />\n<br />\n另一個我們 還深愛著 <br />\n代替我們永恒著 如果能這麼想 就夠了 <br />\n<br />\n同佢攬住聽到呢句 聽到好大力攬實我<br />\n<br />\n最後就靜靜望住佢背影離開直到佢上樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03adfc1a1747ccd9b731c53a7349e9a97c340fcb","tid":2215114,"uid":208940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:47:19.000Z","msg":"苦瓜苦澀嗎？"},{"pid":"49850c2fd18aedc2249950e688aa6f55688fb59d","tid":2215114,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:52:03.000Z","msg":"沒有你<br />\n還是愛你"},{"pid":"4ed65391e1a5d16d6ecba887eb40680290396571","tid":2215114,"uid":314828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T19:57:18.000Z","msg":"綿綿<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f944aa240be48bd0915d049229721932f34937","tid":2215114,"uid":273059,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:09:45.000Z","msg":"不如不見"},{"pid":"b22fecf9fd000caeb25101f424ead4dca0424052","tid":2215114,"uid":132438,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:20:26.000Z","msg":"木紋最尾果段outtro"},{"pid":"8be068515670a6774c81bea75e04c7d5b72ccef2","tid":2215114,"uid":229057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T20:23:53.000Z","msg":"笑容看厭  眼中得缺點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30eaf124bcc1c30ad53d5fd77ddb36168a7e8756","tid":2215114,"uid":2757,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:27:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Y0Ut5ozaKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Y0Ut5ozaKs&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=c4f34aec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Y0Ut5ozaKs</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/x3bDhtuC5yk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fx3bDhtuC5yk&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=5ff6f08d\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/x3bDhtuC5yk</a>"},{"pid":"e1f