瘦<br />\n共你仍舊稱兄呼弟 使這分曖昧更不朽"},{"pid":"d7fa06c12fc8badeb2bca3a8bd0aa15a26e21d8c","tid":2215114,"uid":150556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:49:22.000Z","msg":"遺憾是越努力捉緊這碎片 越難令它重現<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4549d55853edd69f9e1a5d4e87ae803d1e2f5f24","tid":2215114,"uid":367442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b30c5c4bbf905998bb1c60e8cd89cb8f4245c11","tid":2215114,"uid":373590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e934281807439899ea55694a26ec08a771f9166","tid":2215114,"uid":2479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:07:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8lcmmTLOUkg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8lcmmTLOUkg&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFFtf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=5134cab0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8lcmmTLOUkg</a><br />\n最近依首<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"睇咗套戲未 好似好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:57:33.000Z","msg":"睇咗 喊到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506abaa485f632d8d59dc3881a5ae4e1b7cef0e7","tid":2215114,"uid":210071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T06:58:44.000Z","msg":"維持著熟悉表情陌生關係不要變 只等到紅白儀式一場偶遇才會面"}]}